Built in Threat intelligence
Whenever a threat is expereinced by system an alert is created and a short report is built having several sections:
* Overview
* Analyst Report
* Related Incidents 
* Impacted Assets
* prevented Email attempts
* Exposure & mitigations

For comparing security resilience and posture statuses are created as:
* Secure configuration status
* Vulnerability patching status

Threat tags:
* Ransomeware
* Phishing
* Vulnerability
* Activity group
